source.inline: if application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "http://www.youtube.com/watch" or URL starts with "https://www.youtube.com/watch" then					return text 1 thru -11 of (name of t as text)				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn ""

if application "Safari" is running then	tell application "Safari"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "https://music.youtube.com" or URL starts with "http://music.youtube.com" then					try						local groupName, trackName, timeTrack, response						set response to ""						set groupName to do JavaScript "document.getElementsByClassName('byline ytmusic-player-bar')[0]?.firstChild.innerText || ''"						set trackName to do JavaScript "document.getElementsByClassName('title ytmusic-player-bar')[0]?.innerText|| ''"						set timeTrack to do JavaScript "document.getElementsByClassName('time-info ytmusic-player-bar')[0]?.innerText|| ''"												if timeTrack is not equal to "" then							set response to response & "(" & timeTrack & ") "						end if												if groupName is not equal to "" then							set response to response & groupName						end if												if trackName is not equal to "" then							if response is not equal to "" then								set response to response & " - " & trackName							else								set response to response & trackName							end if						end if												if response is equal to "" then return "..........................."						return response					on error errorMsg						return errorMsg					end try				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn ""

actionAppleScript.inline: if application "Safari" is not running then	tell application "Safari" to activateend iftell application "Safari"	repeat with t in tabs of windows		tell t			if URL starts with "https://music.youtube.com" or URL starts with "http://music.youtube.com" then				return			end if		end tell	end repeatend telltell application "Safari" to open location "https://music.youtube.com"

source.inline: tell application "Reminders"	set activeReminders to name of (reminders of list "${YOUR REMINDERS NAME}" whose completed is false)	if activeReminders is not {} then		return some item of activeReminders	else		return ""	end ifend tell

actionAppleScript.inline: activate application "Activity Monitor"tell application "System Events"	tell process "Activity Monitor"		tell radio button "CPU" of radio group 1 of group 2 of toolbar 1 of window 1 to perform action "AXPress"	end tellend tell
tell application "System Events" to keystroke "q" using {control down, command down}
